# General configuraton for yt-dlp

## Include Subtitles

--embed-subs
--sub-langs "ja,zh,zh-CN,zh-Hans,en,de,fr"

## Download-diirectory and filename

-o ~/Downloads/%(channel)s_%(title)s.%(ext)s

## thumbnail

--embed-thumbnail

## Metadata

--embed-metadata

## Chapters and Sponsor-Blocks

--embed-chapters
--sponsorblock-remove "all"

## Video and Audio

### Download and merge the best video-only format and the best audio-only format

-f "bv+ba/b"
--remux-video "mkv"
--merge-output-format "mkv"

### Use the system's dedicated temporary directory for intermediate files

--paths temp:/tmp/yt-dlp_temp

## Browser-Cookies

--cookies-from-browser "chrome"
